Source: mapi
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Jon K Hellan <jon.kare.hellan@uninett.no>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), libnids-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.0

Package: mapi
Architecture: i386
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ucf
Description: Measurement API
 The SCAMPI Measurement API. This API provides a common interface to
 several types of passive monitoring hardware. The package is intended
 for use within UNINETT, the Norwegian national research and education
 network, particularly within the "Målepåle" program.

Package: mapi-dag
Architecture: i386
Depends: dag (>= 3.0.0-1), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ucf, mapi
Conflicts: mapi (<< 1.1.20060904-1)
Description: Endace DAG card driver for Measurement API.
 Endace DAG card driver for the SCAMPI Measurement API. This API provides
 a common interface to several types of passive monitoring hardware. The
 package is intended for use within UNINETT, the Norwegian national 
 research and education network, particularly within the "Målepåle"
 program. 

