Architecture: i386
Depends: dag (>= 3.0.0-1), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ucf, mapi
Conflicts: mapi (<< 1.1.20060904-1)
Description: Napatech NT card driver for Measurement API.
 Napatech NT card driver for the SCAMPI Measurement API. This API 
 provides a common interface to several types of passive monitoring
 hardware. The package is intended for use within UNINETT, the Norwegian
 national research and education network, particularly within the 
 "Målepåle" program. 

